# LaTeX build artifacts. These are regenerated by every `latexmk` run, so
# tracking them produced a merge conflict in each of .aux/.bbl/.log/.fls on top
# of the real one in report.tex. The compiled reports/report.pdf stays tracked
# deliberately -- it is the deliverable.
*.aux
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.out
*.synctex.gz
*.toc
*.lof
*.lot
reports/report.log
reports/build.log

